<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/office-of-the-children-s-commissioner> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Office of the Children’s Commissioner promotes the rights, views and interests of children in policies or decisions affecting their lives. They particularly represent children who are vulnerable or who find it hard to make their views known. Office of the Children's Commissioner is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Education ."@en .
